'''ᱫᱷᱟᱱᱵᱟᱫᱽ''' ᱫᱚ [[ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛ]]ᱤᱭᱟᱹ ᱯᱚᱱᱚᱛ [[ᱡᱷᱟᱨᱠᱷᱚᱸᱰ]] ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱥᱚᱦᱚᱨ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ ᱾<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.merinews.com/catFull.jsp?articleID=127198|title=Eleven Indian cities among 100 fastest growing cities in the world|author=|date=|website=www.merinews.com|accessdate=17 June 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090314000237/http://www.merinews.com/catFull.jsp?articleID=127198|archive-date=14 March 2009|dead-url=no|df=dmy-all}}</ref> ᱡᱷᱟᱨᱠᱷᱚᱸᱰ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱫᱚᱥᱟᱨ ᱟᱹᱰᱤ ᱥᱟᱸᱜᱮ ᱦᱚᱲ ᱮᱞᱮᱞ ᱥᱚᱦᱚᱨ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ ᱾<ref name="auto">{{cite web|url=http://www.census2011.co.in/census/state/jharkhand.html|title=Jharkhand Population Sex Ratio in Jharkhand Literacy rate data|author=|date=|website=www.Census2011.co.in|access-date=17 June 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170618221749/http://www.census2011.co.in/census/state/jharkhand.html|archive-date=18 June 2017|dead-url=no|df=dmy-all}}</ref> ᱫᱷᱟᱱᱵᱟᱫᱽ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱓᱓ ᱟᱱᱟᱜ ᱟᱹᱰᱤ ᱢᱟᱨᱟᱝ ᱥᱚᱦᱚᱨ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ ᱟᱨ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛ ᱨᱮ ᱔᱒ ᱟᱱᱟᱜ ᱟᱹᱰᱤ ᱥᱟᱸᱜᱮ ᱦᱚᱲ ᱮᱞ ᱥᱚᱦᱨᱤ ᱜᱩᱴ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ ᱾ ᱱᱚᱣᱟ ᱟᱞᱜᱟᱛᱮ ᱞᱤᱵᱷᱤᱸᱝ ᱤᱱᱰᱮᱠᱥ ᱨᱮᱸᱠᱤᱸᱧ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱞᱮᱠᱟᱛᱮ ᱙᱔ ᱟᱱᱟᱜ ᱴᱷᱟᱶ ᱨᱮ ᱫᱚᱦᱚ ᱟᱠᱟᱱᱟ ᱾ ᱫᱷᱟᱱᱵᱟᱫᱽ [[ᱟᱥᱟᱱᱥᱳᱞ]], [[ᱯᱚᱪᱷᱤᱢ ᱵᱟᱸᱜᱽᱞᱟ]] ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱥᱟᱞᱟᱜ ᱟᱡᱟᱜ ᱦᱟᱥᱟ ᱥᱤᱢᱟᱹ ᱨᱮ ᱢᱮᱱᱟᱜᱼᱟ ᱾ ᱫᱷᱟᱱᱵᱟᱫᱽ ᱨᱮ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱟᱭᱢᱟ ᱟᱹᱰᱤ ᱢᱟᱨᱟᱝ ᱠᱚᱭᱞᱟ ᱠᱷᱟᱫᱟᱱ ᱢᱮᱱᱟᱜᱼᱟ ᱾<ref>
{{cite news|title=Racketeering in coal: 'Coal crisis' in India presents a highly confusing picture : Cover Story - India Today|url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/racketeering-in-coal-coal-crisis-in-india-presents-a-highly-confusing-picture/1/435040.html|publisher=India Today|date=18 February 2015|access-date=30 January 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170503140557/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/racketeering-in-coal-coal-crisis-in-india-presents-a-highly-confusing-picture/1/435040.html|archive-date=3 May 2017|dead-url=no|df=dmy-all}}
